{"tid":46872,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[成波之路] 朱古力心太軟 (圖文食譜)","createTime":"2016-12-20T03:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T08:40:15.000Z","uid":35319,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a3f8625fb7654fbc14f55a81b346666c8ca97d","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"影片：<a href=\"http://youtu.be/_GfxpwrtiW8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GfxpwrtiW8&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=6f22505d\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/_GfxpwrtiW8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/rDAbowX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDAbowX.jpg&h=3c20c1fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到心太軟，有人會鍾意個流心稀啲有啲似朱古力「汁」<br />\n我就鍾意可以流得慢啲稍為厚身少少既朱古力漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我覺得一定唔可以得個好薄嘅「殼」而食唔到蛋糕<br />\n個蛋糕外層好食都好重要！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁多年嚟做過唔少次心太軟，呢個版本係我自己最滿意嘅一個<br />\n同埋用咗砂糖代替麵粉或者可可粉嚟灑焗杯，除左無咁黐之外，焗出嚟仲會有脆面嘅效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有焗爐嘅不妨試下啦！<br />\n<br />\nFacebook:\t<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9cb37135\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nInstagram:\t<a href=\"http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fmywaystogetfat&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a6c69d56\" target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/mywaystogetfat</a><br />\nBlog:\t\t<a href=\"http://www.mywaystogetfat.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mywaystogetfat.com&d=XH28pMGT6MRyCCb5fGXV9XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=9c9656fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mywaystogetfat.com</a><br />\n<strong>Blog 可以睇返之前出過post既食譜</strong><br />\n有興趣請like/follow/睇睇啦，多謝你既留意同支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>份量：2 杯<br />\n<ins>材料</ins></strong>\t<br />\nNonstick Cooking Spray 或 牛油溶液（掃焗杯用）\t適量<br />\n砂糖（灑焗杯用）\t適量<br />\n60%黑朱古力\t60 克<br />\n無鹽牛油\t40 克<br />\n即溶咖啡粉\t1/4 茶匙<br />\n鹽\t1/8 茶匙<br />\n蛋液\t70 克<br />\n砂糖\t35 克<br />\n?酒\t1 1/2 茶匙<br />\n雲呢拿香油\t1/2 茶匙<br />\n中筋麵粉\t30 克<br />\n糖霜（灑面用）\t適量"},{"pid":"1b6ddc3275518eab345110d6f9c838d03f261113","tid":46872,"uid":38461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8b9247be5f00fd581be910d0a00da01712e3d4","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"1. 把Nonstick Cooking Spray噴在焗杯中再用掃掃開，或在焗杯中掃上牛油溶液。然後灑入適量砂糖，轉動焗杯令焗杯內側都黏上砂糖，再倒出多餘的砂糖，備用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/Dwrd9zM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDwrd9zM.jpg&h=2f9b4fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 把60%黑朱古力、無鹽牛油、即溶咖啡粉和鹽放到不鏽鋼或玻璃碗中。把碗架在熱水上，碗底不要直接碰到水面。以小火保持熱水溫度，待黑朱古力和牛油溶化，拌勻備用。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/86P80nq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F86P80nq.jpg&h=d6ef51f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 打散雞蛋量出 70 毫升蛋液。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/Qq9h98q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQq9h98q.jpg&h=04822ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 把砂糖倒入蛋液中，以打蛋器打至發泡及淡黃色，不需要打發至企身。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/0wrK93d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0wrK93d.jpg&h=5d34c4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 把步驟 2 的朱古力牛油混合物、?酒和雲呢拿香油加入步驟 4 中拌勻。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/be3y17t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbe3y17t.jpg&h=a64af1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 加入中筋麵粉拌至不見乾粉即成蛋糕漿。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/rs99k59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frs99k59.jpg&h=da3dac3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 把蛋糕漿平均倒入焗杯中，放入已預熱至攝氏 220 度的焗爐中下層，焗 8 分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/X9BcBT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX9BcBT4.jpg&h=ee20f187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 焗好後立即取出，以小刀於蛋糕外圍貼著杯子劃一圈，然後倒扣在碟上，灑上糖霜即成。<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/fdPOHEi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfdPOHEi.jpg&h=ced4f923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 我的焗杯是 9cm 直徑的梳乎厘焗杯。如用不同大小形狀的容器需要調整時間。<br />\n- 如第一次做任何心太軟食譜，建議先焗一杯試好爐溫時間，雖然焗過火還是可以焗出好吃的朱古力蛋糕來，但沒流心就不是心太軟了！<br />\n- 如想蛋糕表面的砂糖不要那麼明顯，可用糖粉Caster Sugar代替灑焗杯用的糖。"},{"pid":"9321686f950dc3ef23f9daa124959223537c8f6d","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8946e671da8d873997496f6081217c490909b6fd","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蛋液應該係70毫升，唔是70克<br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f1f80e3da429cb643c2fa7f080572f34e13d4026","tid":46872,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T03:47:45.000Z","msg":"你總是心太軟，心太軟"},{"pid":"2a043a15952045608399ce7fd42731c8695882bb","tid":46872,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:01:15.000Z","msg":"波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337d557099abb845aa9098ec33318825775c05e1","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你總是心太軟，心太軟</blockquote><br />\n好老套呀大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9fa04175a42090b859234fdba4e8f57fb8db1d","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />C cup sister"},{"pid":"cb51cd7cf234f49203daf609f9c3be7c8b5f71b1","tid":46872,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"好易啲牛油分離左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw有冇綠茶心太軟recipe"},{"pid":"fe28630c832e05258438cac54eb7e0eee49f3d98","tid":46872,"uid":41959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"93e94a6ee05d3ac785c1b8ea1f65865d9f15b586","tid":46872,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T06:01:32.000Z","msg":"有睇開你煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如你煮餐好既比平仔食啊，見佢日日都食魚飯食到狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62fb610b7b363bc52b8e0b34facf276358304b4","tid":46872,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:49:18.000Z","msg":"呢隻顏色嘅外殼似好食<br />\n好黑嗰d多數好甜"},{"pid":"1b09c1eca9d744cdfe0fde265d7cc3f3291d30d5","tid":46872,"uid":30698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"4a37a172fbcc84766555769acffdc81eb6b45000","tid":46872,"uid":45128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n望到你落左好多糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36861f2891fe1bececaeb252046e696edfc3dc25","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好易啲牛油分離左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw有冇綠茶心太軟recipe</blockquote><br />\n整呢個好少有呢個問題喎<br />\n你指加朱古力牛油落去蛋果度果陣？"},{"pid":"eec0aa5a0eefa0a891bc1b09abda3c7f520c526a","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好易啲牛油分離左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw有冇綠茶心太軟recipe</blockquote><br />\n呀漏咗第二個問題<br />\n抹茶味嘅話我無試真寫過食譜POST<br />\n大約係將黑朱古力變成白朱古力<br />\n然後將糖減到好少量<br />\n將少部份嘅麵粉轉做抹茶粉（10克內）<br />\n唔好落咖啡粉<br />\n大約係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674d4237c8af8422bf979f908c4627e13bde7aad","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0f16589a13a6c901c99c92ed2fa0efb71efc00","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有睇開你煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如你煮餐好既比平仔食啊，見佢日日都食魚飯食到狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你呀有睇呀！<br />\n請問而家果位二哥係唔係真係二哥嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23d341592ae688affba0d4b3c9b81faf2a3c434e","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻顏色嘅外殼似好食<br />\n好黑嗰d多數好甜</blockquote><br />\n我諗黑唔黑關係在用咩濃度朱古力同埋朱古力同其他材料嘅比例？唔關甜唔甜事？"},{"pid":"ef71ab310f28f2b2f34fb052387d59ca7377eb7f","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6fbdfd6648f2b8e51cbf9908bad25a8ced076b","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n望到你落左好多糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多嘢都好多糖，爭在自己睇唔睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甜品嚟講，呢個落糖唔算好誇張喇<br />\n怕糖唔好整甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56aeea0dd2df4d4d52f937ee25f4603f4b1d8d8","tid":46872,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09feb46300c4ee828db1ecff3fa24fda81b7e46a","tid":46872,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"試過諗住整心太軟 唔小心加得太大火力 變咗做蛋糕"},{"pid":"124c632785b6a8aed17b9de8051e2bbd04d01eb5","tid":46872,"uid":55120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ecdbc2f7fce4d4f45965f6357a832bb573eb01b8","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順手沖廁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634b6ab17377490fa496d3ee1e2b9372c7369e54","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過諗住整心太軟 唔小心加得太大火力 變咗做蛋糕</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係第一次做嘅食譜或者第一次用個爐，好容易就會咁<br />\n<br />\n最好第一次做放入爐就計時，set高溫，望住佢焗，蛋糕會開始焗成形<br />\n多數焗到面頭唔再係漿，外圍一圈熟咗同脹起，中心仲係凹果陣就要收手，仲要快啲拎出嚟同上碟，因為咁細個蛋糕，餘溫都好易整熟佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成功嘅就記低焗咗幾耐幾多度<br />\n<br />\n不過就算熟晒，都好食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好太介意"},{"pid":"a38d82c590fda127cb6ce461fe80b31d7103a07c","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b183fddf082b7c887e8df350d1dc6310adc04e3","tid":46872,"uid":35754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"lum酒？"},{"pid":"093af77529890e4b07219aaa7e42546d11ced176","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lum酒？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我而家先見到唔記得改果個？<br />\n係呀<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係冧酒　唔係?酒呀！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src