Time":"2016-12-21T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己整成本大約幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f8642091cc00853b501820d1b0f53985f1270b","tid":46872,"uid":22733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"強帖留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由高登追到連登<br />\n之前跟你整果個煙肉墨西哥辣椒個個食完讚不絕口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油出多啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a327268fd289bbdccd727dd31fcef7e1d281126a","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8251a96bdc1f1a1877079b9b241fe97a0cad1b4b","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7459b630bbbd024d759ec2989fe33e01d75be5","tid":46872,"uid":67195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:07:52.000Z","msg":"多謝師姐救我一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443375c08df8e14c8adef24adebdabd732535d02","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己整成本大約幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果淨係計材料嘅話，當本身屋企乜都無，要由頭買起，大部份價錢以某烘焙店咁計：<br />\n牛油100克 - $14<br />\n砂糖1磅 - $8.5<br />\nValrhona 61%黑朱古力磚200克 - $42.5(有平啲揀嘅如果要...)<br />\n無糖咖啡粉20克 - $7<br />\n鹽 - 無計<br />\n雞蛋2隻- 當$4<br />\n冧酒100mL - $20.0<br />\n雲尼拿香油30毫升 - $10 (建議買好少少唔好用呢啲人做嘢)<br />\n中筋麵粉1公斤 - $16.5<br />\n糖霜250克 - $6<br />\n總數：$128.5 加幾粒鹽<br />\n未計用具<br />\n<br />\n（純有感而發，唔是針對巴打你，唔好介意！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔係話巴打你！！！我認得你個名唔係第一次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你）<br />\n<br />\n有時聽到啲人話「出面食XXX要$XXX，我自己整只係$XXX就整到」<br />\n或者有時係「出面食XXX先$XX，自己買料都要$XXX仲自己整好ON9」<br />\n其實聽到我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其果啲話出面食咩咩好貴返屋企整好平，然後仲要話人呃錢果啲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如果由頭買一次材料整可能有人會覺得百幾蚊出去食都得<br />\n唔好講果啲咩淨低啲材料可以整多幾多次或者再變乜野出嚟果啲ON9婆乸數喇<br />\n其實我自己整嘢食純粹因為自己想整同埋想食<br />\n畀百幾蚊，有得食﹑有得玩，我覺好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己整，其實有部份原因都係想用好啲材料，唔好為咗慳買啲低質嘢<br />\n想慳可以煮多啲，長遠計會慳咗，又食好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69b6d90aa30d9e1bc749734817ed3df560ed65b","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強帖留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由高登追到連登<br />\n之前跟你整果個煙肉墨西哥辣椒個個食完讚不絕口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油出多啲post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀，多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果味最難都係買果條jalapeno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買到就成功咗大半，哈哈"},{"pid":"a51127f141159c7ee760d39d0cc3b7ee4086b44d","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝師姐救我一命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHOW???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fa4744074ddc4e23a6b2b1167ac0f29fee095e","tid":46872,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" 