kgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來成本都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28248997f6af6eace296dcaa5816cf028b8060d","tid":46872,"uid":35319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T11:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己整成本大約幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果淨係計材料嘅話，當本身屋企乜都無，要由頭買起，大部份價錢以某烘焙店咁計：<br />\n牛油100克 - $14<br />\n砂糖1磅 - $8.5<br />\nValrhona 61%黑朱古力磚200克 - $42.5(有平啲揀嘅如果要...)<br />\n無糖咖啡粉20克 - $7<br />\n鹽 - 無計<br />\n雞蛋2隻- 當$4<br />\n冧酒100mL - $20.0<br />\n雲尼拿香油30毫升 - $10 (建議買好少少唔好用呢啲人做嘢)<br />\n中筋麵粉1公斤 - $16.5<br />\n糖霜250克 - $6<br />\n總數：$128.5 加幾粒鹽<br />\n未計用具<br />\n<br />\n（純有感而發，唔是針對巴打你，唔好介意！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔係話巴打你！！！我認得你個名唔係第一次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你）<br />\n<br />\n有時聽到啲人話「出面食XXX要$XXX，我自己整只係$XXX就整到」<br />\n或者有時係「出面食XXX先$XX，自己買料都要$XXX仲自己整好ON9」<br />\n其實聽到我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其果啲話出面食咩咩好貴返屋企整好平，然後仲要話人呃錢果啲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如果由頭買一次材料整可能有人會覺得百幾蚊出去食都得<br />\n唔好講果啲咩淨低啲材料可以整多幾多次或者再變乜野出嚟果啲ON9婆乸數喇<br />\n其實我自己整嘢食純粹因為自己想整同埋想食<br />\n畀百幾蚊，有得食﹑有得玩，我覺好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己整，其實有部份原因都係想用好啲材料，唔好為咗慳買啲低質嘢<br />\n想慳可以煮多啲，長遠計會慳咗，又食好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來成本都唔平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買多隻蛋呢堆嘢整到四杯仲有嘢淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我驚食唔晒所以整咗兩杯<br />\n整出嚟果份成功感是無價的巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冧到條女仲唔抵返晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f5c759b01b911b3c688f0782c3f97182a6aac2","tid":46872,"uid":4502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果淨係計材料嘅話，當本身屋企乜都無，要由頭買起，大部份價錢以某烘焙店咁計：<br />\n牛油100克 - $14<br />\n砂糖1磅 - $8.5<br />\nValrhona 61%黑朱古力磚200克 - $42.5(有平啲揀嘅如果要...)<br />\n無糖咖啡粉20克 - $7<br />\n鹽 - 無計<br />\n雞蛋2隻- 當$4<br />\n冧酒100mL - $20.0<br />\n雲尼拿香油30毫升 - $10 (建議買好少少唔好用呢啲人做嘢)<br />\n中筋麵粉1公斤 - $16.5<br />\n糖霜250克 - $6<br />\n總數：$128.5 加幾粒鹽<br />\n未計用具<br />\n<br />\n（純有感而發，唔是針對巴打你，唔好介意！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔係話巴打你！！！我認得你個名唔係第一次出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝你）<br />\n<br />\n有時聽到啲人話「出面食XXX要$XXX，我自己整只係$XXX就整到」<br />\n或者有時係「出面食XXX先$XX，自己買料都要$XXX仲自己整好ON9」<br />\n其實聽到我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其果啲話出面食咩咩好貴返屋企整好平，然後仲要話人呃錢果啲&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n如果由頭買一次材料整可能有人會覺得百幾蚊出去食都得<br />\n唔好講果啲咩淨低啲材料可以整多幾多